      "instruction": "<p>While the orecchiette is cooking, peel and slice (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>and <strong>tomato paste </strong>in 250ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [325ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
